snippet.title: Tic Tac Tanks Release Trailer: A Tactical Coffee Break Puzzle Game
snippet.description:
Tic Tac Tanks is a coffee break puzzle game with toy-like visuals.

Thanks for checking out Tic Tac Tanks Trailer!

The game will launch on March 31st, 2022, for $5 on itch.io.

Sign-up with this link to be notified right when the game goes live: https://www.heartgamedev.com/tic-tac-tanks

Thank you all so much for your support!
